wiki.summary: "Stargirl Interlude" is the eighth track from The Weeknd's third studio album, Starboy. It features Lana Del Rey. The title of the track is a reference to the success of Abel as a "Starboy", who happens to need a superwoman to complete him. However, the lyrics are mysterious in nature and Del Rey starts off low and ends high, The Weeknd closing off the 2-minute interlude. Read more on Last.fm.
